flowchart TD
    A[Intake] --> B[Manager Loop Start]
    B --> C[Select Next Action]
    C --> D[Delegate Worker Task]
    D --> E[Checkpoint + State Update]
    E --> F{Progress Adequate?}
    F -->|Yes| G{Gates Passed?}
    F -->|No| H[Replan / Reroute]
    H --> C
    G -->|Yes| I[Finalize]
    G -->|No| J[Repair / Escalate]
